domains2idna
=============


The tool to convert domains to the famous IDNA format.
------------------------------------------------------

.. image:: https://travis-ci.com/PyFunceble/domain2idna.svg?branch=master
    :target: https://travis-ci.com/PyFunceble/domain2idna
